message.content: cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper deals with Visual Question Answering (VQA), which involves training an intelligent system to answer questions about images. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel keyword extraction method, which involves designing discriminative decoders, indicating the use of machine learning techniques, and falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves text processing and information retrieval, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
